   Accueil>>>A 94 kb genomic sequence 3′ to the murine Xist gene reveals
   an AT rich region containing a new testis specific gene Tsx.

A 94 kb genomic sequence 3′ to the murine Xist gene reveals an AT rich region
containing a new testis specific gene Tsx.

   Hum Mol Genet 1996 Nov;5(11):1713-26.

Tutelles

   Centre National de la Recherche Scientifique
